article.description: Nate Pierre-Louis posted 19 points as Temple beat Morgan State 75-57 on Saturday.
article.headline: Pierre-Louis lifts Temple past Morgan St. 75-57
article.linkText: Pierre-Louis lifts Temple past Morgan St. 75-57
article.story: PHILADELPHIA -- Nate Pierre-Louis posted 19 points as Temple beat Morgan State 75-57 on Saturday. Quinton Rose had 16 points for Temple (2-0). Alani Moore II added 14 points. De'Vondre Perry had 12 points for the home team. Sherwyn Devonish-Prince Jr. had 12 points for the Bears (1-1). Isaiah Burke added 11 points. Stanley Davis had 10 points. Temple faces La Salle on the road next Saturday. Morgan State plays St. Francis (Pa.) at home on Wednesday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
